OL,3,CInside the only factory where milk is
OL,4,Cproduced, bottled and sold in Wales
OL,6,FPembrokeshire Creamery is opening its
OL,7,Fbrand new milk processing facility in
OL,8,FHaverfordwest.
OL,10,FIt's the only liquid milk facility in
OL,11,FWales certified to supply major
OL,12,Fretailers and has been built to ensure
OL,13,Fthat Welsh milk no longer needs to be
OL,14,Fsent to England for processing.
OL,16,FEndaf Edwards is the Site Lead at
OL,17,FPembrokeshire Creamery, he says the
OL,18,Faim is to produce milk that is
OL,19,Fproduced, bottled and sold in Wales:
