OL,3,CInside the only factory where milk is
OL,4,Cproduced, bottled and sold in Wales
OL,6,F"I think it's very important for us as
OL,7,Fa company but it's very important for
OL,8,FWales as a whole.
OL,10,F"It's all clearly produced in Wales.
OL,11,FIt gets processed in the factory, it
OL,12,Fgets bottled in the factory and it's
OL,13,Fout to the retailers of only Wales.
OL,15,F"So, our ethos and our USP is we get
OL,16,Fall the milk that's produced in Wales,
OL,17,Fto be bottled in Wales and sold in
OL,18,FWales."
