OL,6,FWhen asked about the scope of job
OL,7,Fopportunities for people of Wales and
OL,8,Fthe impact it will have to the
OL,9,Fagricultural industry in Wales, Mr
OL,10,FEdwards said:
OL,12,F"I think it's a big importance to be
OL,13,Ffair for agriculture as there's no
OL,14,Fother fresh bottle in sight with a BRC
OL,15,Faccreditation that's feeding fresh
OL,16,Fmilk bottles into the retail.
OL,18,F"The tankers are driving 650-700 miles
OL,19,Fas a round trip. The importance is
OL,20,Fthat it stays in Wales.
