OL,6,F"Give us consistency and give us
OL,7,Fsustainability and for farmers it's
OL,8,Fimportance to understand that it's
OL,9,Fsomebody local looking after their
OL,10,Fwell being."
OL,12,FHe added: "We are shareholders of this
OL,13,Fbusiness and we went about things the
OL,14,Fright way, we've brought experience
OL,15,Ffrom the liquid dairy industry.
OL,17,F"There is a clear gap in the market,
OL,18,Fbringing it back to that. Farmers are
OL,19,Fbuying into that.
